	usage of verbose-categories and -output-stream.
	* src/dlvhex/DependencyGraph.cpp (componentFinder): Likewise.
	* src/dlvhex/PluginContainer.cpp (importPlugin): Likewise.
	* src/dlvhex/SafetyChecker.cpp (throw): Likewise.

